               type="paratext">Betr. <rs ref="#pmb11988"
                  type="person">Kraus</rs> – <rs ref="#pmb10364"
                  type="person">Viertel</rs>
               <lb xml:id="uuid_f1f8f5c2-b6fb-44a8-a485-2c2049293541"/>exp. 12.5.1930.</note></p>
